        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="nwxjK7dy7dN10PqU6JS9-21" parent="1" style="sketch=0;outlineConnect=0;fontColor=#232F3E;fillColor=#01A88D;strokeColor=#ffffff;dashed=0;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;verticalAlign=top;align=center;html=1;fontSize=10;fontStyle=0;aspect=fixed;shape=mxgraph.aws4.resourceIcon;resIcon=mxgraph.aws4.bedrock_agentcore;" value="AWS Config Specialist&#xa;Nova 2 Lite" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="60" x="570" y="660" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="nwxjK7dy7dN10PqU6JS9-22" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="PrivateSubnet2  · us-east-1b&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Agents via ENI in VPC" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="40" width="180" x="460" y="410" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="nwxjK7dy7dN10PqU6JS9-23" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="PrivateSubnet1 · us-east-1a&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Functions via ENI in VPC" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="40" width="160" x="140" y="410" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="nwxjK7dy7dN10PqU6JS9-24" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F0F4F8;strokeColor=#3A6FA5;fontSize=11;fontStyle=0;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Traffic flows&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;1. Team member browser → CloudFront (https://.cloudfront.net) → S3 UI bucket (OAC) — serves the SPA (index.html + JS/CSS bundle).&lt;br&gt;2. SPA loads → reads sessionStorage tokens → if missing redirects to /signin → user clicks Sign In → Cognito Hosted UI (poc-st21arbiter.auth) → Authorization Code flow → /callback exchanges code for IdToken + access_token + refresh_token.&lt;br&gt;3. SPA decodes IdToken locally → reads cognito:groups claim → pins personaId in PersonaContext →  permits or denies each route per the matrix above.&lt;br&gt;4. SPA → API Gateway with Bearer JWT (Cognito authorizer) for short ops: GET /findings, GET /actions, GET /audit, GET /conversations[?type=analyst|mcp], GET /conversations/{id}, GET /conversations/{id}/messages.&lt;br&gt;5. SPA → Lambda Function URL with Bearer JWT (manual JWT decode in Lambda) for /chat. Bypasses API GW&#39;s 29s integration timeout for long agent fan-outs.&lt;br&gt;6. api_handler Lambda → AgentCore InvokeAgentRuntime on the master orchestrator (sync). Master uses Strands tools sharepoint_lookup / awsconfig_lookup / zscaler_lookup → each fans out to its specialist runtime.&lt;br&gt;7. Master + specialists run Nova 2 Lite via Bedrock ConverseStream. KB retrievals hit the Bedrock KB → OpenSearch Serverless vector index policy-vectors (sourced from S3 processed bucket ingestion).&lt;br&gt;8. Master writes the session row to DDB sessions table (with chat_type=&quot;analyst&quot;|&quot;mcp&quot;) on first turn; bumps last_message_at + message_count each turn. AgentCore Memory stores the full event history (90-day TTL).&lt;br&gt;9. CodeBuild (arm64) builds agent images on deploy_agents.py runs; pushes to ECR; AgentCore Runtime pulls on update.&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="300" width="1270" x="40" y="998" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="nwxjK7dy7dN10PqU6JS9-33" parent="1" style="sketch=0;outlineConnect=0;fontColor=#232F3E;fillColor=#7AA116;strokeColor=#ffffff;dashed=0;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;verticalAlign=top;align=center;html=1;fontSize=10;fontStyle=0;aspect=fixed;shape=mxgraph.aws4.resourceIcon;resIcon=mxgraph.aws4.s3;" value="cfn-templates" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="50" width="50" x="1114.66" y="896" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
